    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade example that defines the 'mint' standard. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, retaining its deep, glass-like factory finish with a professional ceramic coating and zero road rash or swirl marks. The interior remains in showroom state, featuring supple, unscuffed leather and high-grade materials that still carry a hint of the new-car scent; every button, dial, and digital display functions with tactical precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a fully documented history of preventative maintenance with all original manuals and two sets of keys included. From the spotless engine bay to the pristine undercarriage, this car offers a turn-key experience for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection without compromise.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
