    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle exemplifies automotive excellence. Meticulously maintained and preserved in a pristine state, it offers an unparalleled driving experience for the discerning collector. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior upholstery, reflects a standard of care rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a top-tier specimen that performs with the precision of a new machine.",
